This paper is primarily focused on natural language understanding for intelligent agents, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of deep neural network architectures and transfer learning also suggests a strong connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the evaluation of the proposed methods on new domains, which could potentially fall under software engineering (cs.SE) or natural language processing (cs.NE).
